Your Highness the Crown Prince, excuse this old minister for speaking straightforwardly.

5
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:40,030
The imperial exam system is the foundation of the nation.

6
00:01:40,030 --> 00:01:43,380
It's an important event for the country to search of talented people.

7
00:01:43,380 --> 00:01:46,940
Furthermore, Your Majesty's health is weak

8
00:01:46,940 --> 00:01:51,890
