616
00:42:40,050 --> 00:42:43,460
Duke of Hedong's heir deliberately found out about your family's background.

617
00:42:43,460 --> 00:42:45,820
I happened to see it.

618
00:42:47,500 --> 00:42:51,270
Anyone here? Anyone here?

619
00:42:51,270 --> 00:42:53,930
Madam Cao, have you come here by mistake?

620
00:42:53,930 --> 00:42:55,410
Or is it like your daughter,

621
00:42:55,410 --> 00:42:57,970
