622
00:42:57,970 --> 00:43:00,760
I came here to find her!

623
00:43:01,840 --> 00:43:03,780
Move aside!

624
00:43:20,700 --> 00:43:25,000
You really look like your mother, another foxy tramp.

625
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:28,540
Your mother made the Kudi family into a chaotic state back then.

626
00:43:28,540 --> 00:43:31,420
Now you want to come and ruin your younger sister's marriage. Isn't that right?

627
00:43:31,420 --> 00:43:34,080
Your daughter came in here on her own.

628
00:43:34,080 --> 00:43:37,360
She stole the design that I made for Madam Pei Yan.

629
00:43:37,360 --> 00:43:40,280
That's why she got embarrassed at the flower pageant.

